What is the requirement of Looping?

• If We want to repeat one or more than one line of code repeatedly then we required Looping

• Looping is also known as Repetition or Iteration

There are two types of loop in python --> For
                                      --> while
While Loop:-

In loop we require 3 things:-   (3S rule)
    Start Value
    Stop Value
    Step Value

SYNTAX:-
            initialization
            while Condition:
                Statement
                Increment/Decrement
